Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.910
Parch &amp; Posey sotuvlar menejeri uchun,

00:00:02.910 --> 00:00:06.674
buyurtmalarni umumiy guruhlarga ajratish foydali mashqdir.

00:00:06.674 --> 00:00:11.220
Ammo har bir guruhdagi barcha buyurtmalarni hisoblashga imkon bersangiz yana ham foydaliroq bo‘ladi.

00:00:11.220 --> 00:00:14.474
Ushbu toifalarga ko‘ra agregatlash kompaniya rahbarlariga

00:00:14.474 --> 00:00:18.695
qayta ma’lumot yetkazish va chora ko‘rishni osonlashtiradi.

00:00:18.695 --> 00:00:20.429
Barcha guruh a’zolarini hisoblashning eng oson yo‘li

00:00:20.429 --> 00:00:24.480
siz xohlaga tarzda guruhlaydigan yangi ustunni yaratishdir,

00:00:24.480 --> 00:00:28.214
keyin ushbu guruh tomonidan hisoblash uchun boshqa yangi ustun yarating.

00:00:28.214 --> 00:00:35.162
Bu yerda biz CASE dan 500 dan yuqori, 500 va 500 dan kam miqdorda,

00:00:35.162 --> 00:00:38.960
buyurtmalarni guruhlash uchun foydalanamiz.

00:00:38.960 --> 00:00:41.225
Ushbu so‘rov GROUP BY da to‘liq ustunli hisob-kitoblarning

00:00:41.225 --> 00:00:44.210
o‘rniga raqamlarni ishlatish uchun yaxshi joy,

00:00:44.210 --> 00:00:45.890
chunki GROUP BY da CASE bayonotini takrorlash

00:00:45.890 --> 00:00:48.935
so‘rovni juda ham uzoq qilib yuborardi.

00:00:48.935 --> 00:00:50.329
Hozir, sizz o‘ylayotgan bo‘lishingiz mumkin,

00:00:50.329 --> 00:00:54.770
Nima uchun men hisoblashni xohlamagan qatorlarni filtrlash uchun WHERE bandidan foydalanmayman?

00:00:54.770 --> 00:00:56.475
Siz buni amalga oshirishingiz mumkin edi,

00:00:56.475 --> 00:01:08.200
va u bunday ko‘rinishda bo‘lardi.

00:01:08.200 --> 00:01:14.996
Afsuski, WHERE bandidan foydalanish bir vaqtda faqat bitta shartni hisoblash imkonini beradi.

00:01:14.996 --> 00:01:17.905
Agar biz turli xil holatlarga duch kelsak, bu zerikarli bo‘lar edi.

00:01:17.905 --> 00:01:20.000
Bizga har biri uchun alohida so‘rov kerak bo‘lardi.

